Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.78,0:00:04.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,40歳という大人にとっては\N２年というのは
Dialogue: 9,0:00:00.94,0:00:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,To a forty-year-old adult, two years\Nmight not make much of a difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.80,0:00:08.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さほどの意味を持たない\N歳月かもしれない
Dialogue: 9,0:00:08.29,0:00:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,At most, their hair might turn a little grayer, their body might lose a bit of vigor,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.79,0:00:12.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,せいぜい ちょっぴり髪の毛が\N白くなり 体に締まりがなくなり
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.79,0:00:15.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ほんの少し 息切れがしやすくなる
Dialogue: 9,0:00:13.34,0:00:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,and they might lose their breath more easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.78,0:00:20.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それが２年という月日の\N平均的な効果だろう
Dialogue: 9,0:00:16.20,0:00:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,That’s what happens to most in two years time.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.80,0:00:25.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だが 12歳の少年少女にとって\N２年というのは
Dialogue: 9,0:00:21.21,0:00:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,But for children twelve years of age,
Dialogue: 9,0:00:24.78,0:00:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,two years is more than enough to bring about drastic changes, regardless of their era.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.77,0:00:28.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いつの時代も\N劇的な変化をもたらすのに
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.79,0:00:32.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,十分な時間である
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.78,0:00:37.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,早季～っ！
Dialogue: 9,0:00:35.68,0:00:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Saki!
Dialogue: 9,0:00:38.58,0:00:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez, I told you to wait for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.77,0:00:40.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もう 待っててって言ったのに
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.80,0:00:43.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ごめん ごめん\N教室にいなかったから
Dialogue: 9,0:00:41.17,0:00:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, sorry.
Dialogue: 9,0:00:42.61,0:00:45.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You weren’t in the classroom, so\NI figured you might’ve gone ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.77,0:00:45.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,先に行っちゃったかなと思って
Dialogue: 9,0:00:45.59,0:00:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.79,0:00:47.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,んっ も～っ…\Nごめんてば
Dialogue: 9,0:00:46.84,0:00:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I said I’m sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.76,0:00:49.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ちゃんと見たの？
Dialogue: 9,0:00:48.32,0:00:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you take a good look?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.81,0:00:51.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,見たよ～
Dialogue: 9,0:00:49.88,0:00:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.79,0:01:07.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あらあら 覚と瞬も\N相変わらず仲のいいこと
Dialogue: 9,0:01:03.54,0:01:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at that.
Dialogue: 9,0:01:04.33,0:01:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Satoru and Shun are as happy together as ever.
Dialogue: 9,0:01:07.63,0:01:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.78,0:01:09.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,よっ\Nやあ
Dialogue: 9,0:01:08.48,0:01:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.78,0:01:15.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,早季？
Dialogue: 9,0:01:13.88,0:01:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Saki.
Dialogue: 9,0:01:15.57,0:01:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm? What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.79,0:01:17.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,え？ 何 どうしたの？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.79,0:01:20.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何でもないわ
Dialogue: 9,0:01:19.35,0:01:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 9,0:01:23.73,0:01:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,We had all turned fourteen.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.79,0:01:26.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,皆 14歳になっていた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.56,0:01:31.98,TS-EpTitle8,,0,0,0,,{\fad(987,0)\xshad10.000000\yshad5.000000\an6\blur0.84\fs66.000000\pos(861.000000,69.000000)}Episode Eight
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.56,0:01:31.98,TS-EpTitle8,,0,0,0,,{\fad(987,0)\xshad10.000000\yshad5.000000\blur0.84\fs66.000000\an4\pos(957.000000,69.000000)}Omen
Dialogue: 9,0:01:43.45,0:01:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Saki, check this out.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.71,0:01:45.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,早季 ほら どうよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.73,0:01:54.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ちょっと ゆがんでるんじゃない？
Dialogue: 9,0:01:52.87,0:01:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn’t it a bit distorted?
Dialogue: 9,0:01:54.45,0:01:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Are you kidding me?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.75,0:01:57.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はあ～？ 何 言ってんだよ\N完璧な平面だろ
Dialogue: 9,0:01:56.17,0:01:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s perfectly flat!
Dialogue: 9,0:01:57.51,0:02:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The middle of my face isn’t that sunken-in!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.75,0:01:59.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私の顔\Nこんなに しゃくれてないわ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.72,0:02:02.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何だよ ゆがんでんのは\Nお前の心の方だろ？
Dialogue: 9,0:02:00.06,0:02:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Isn’t it {\i1}your{\i0} heart that’s distorted here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.72,0:02:05.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ウフフッ…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.75,0:02:10.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,えいっ！\N…って～ てめ～！
Dialogue: 9,0:02:08.81,0:02:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch! You little—
Dialogue: 9,0:02:10.70,0:02:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I didn’t see you there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.73,0:02:13.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あ～ら ごめん 気がつかなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.74,0:02:19.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうだい？ ヒナが\N形成される感触はあるかい？
Dialogue: 9,0:02:17.20,0:02:20.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Well? Can you feel the chick in its egg, growing and taking shape?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.71,0:02:23.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いえ まだなんとなくって感じです
Dialogue: 9,0:02:20.49,0:02:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,No, all I have so far is this vague feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.73,0:02:28.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,かなり高度な課題だからね\Nだが 青沼君なら大丈夫だろう
Dialogue: 9,0:02:24.19,0:02:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s a challenging task, to be sure.
Dialogue: 9,0:02:26.57,0:02:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But if anybody can do it, it’s you, Aonuma-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.72,0:02:31.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,早く かわいいヒヨコを\N見せてほしいなあ
Dialogue: 9,0:02:28.96,0:02:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Please let me see that adorable little chick soon.
Dialogue: 9,0:02:40.13,0:02:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Shun!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.75,0:02:42.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,瞬…
Dialogue: 9,0:02:42.72,0:02:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,How is it? Going well?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.75,0:02:45.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どう うまくいってる？\Nばっちり ばっちり
Dialogue: 9,0:02:44.71,0:02:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Piece of cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.72,0:02:48.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,凄いね\N何 言ってんだよ
Dialogue: 9,0:02:46.36,0:02:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You’re really good.
Dialogue: 9,0:02:47.29,0:02:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.75,0:02:53.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,瞬の課題に比べたら全然\N２時間で羽化させるんだろ～？
Dialogue: 9,0:02:48.98,0:02:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s nothing compared to your task.
Dialogue: 9,0:02:51.66,0:02:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to hatch it in two hours, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.73,0:02:55.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんなことないよ
Dialogue: 9,0:02:53.84,0:02:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You’re exaggerating.
Dialogue: 9,0:02:55.54,0:02:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone expects great things from you, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.74,0:02:57.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,瞬への期待度は半端ないからな～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.73,0:03:04.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いっつ…
Dialogue: 9,0:03:04.36,0:03:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Want to go to the infirmary?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.72,0:03:06.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,保健室 行く？
Dialogue: 9,0:03:06.53,0:03:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.72,0:03:08.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,大丈夫 たいしたことないから
Dialogue: 9,0:03:07.71,0:03:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s just a little cut.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.74,0:03:11.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ちょっと見せて どれどれ
Dialogue: 9,0:03:09.42,0:03:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me see.
Dialogue: 9,0:03:10.67,0:03:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.73,0:03:14.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,う～ん… 血は平気かもね～
Dialogue: 9,0:03:12.93,0:03:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The bleeding shouldn’t be too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.74,0:03:40.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,すばる～！
Dialogue: 9,0:03:39.17,0:03:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Subaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.74,0:03:46.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,って ことは…？
Dialogue: 9,0:03:43.91,0:03:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,This must mean…
Dialogue: 9,0:03:46.43,0:03:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Subaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.74,0:03:48.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,すばる～！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.74,0:03:55.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やっぱり！
Dialogue: 9,0:03:53.92,0:03:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,There he is!
Dialogue: 9,0:03:57.67,0:03:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Shun!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.72,0:03:59.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,待ってよ 瞬！\Nうわっ
Dialogue: 9,0:03:59.59,0:04:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Got you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.74,0:04:01.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,捕まえた！ アハハハ…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.74,0:04:16.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,離せよ
Dialogue: 9,0:04:15.87,0:04:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Let go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.74,0:04:18.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,イヤだって言ったら？
Dialogue: 9,0:04:17.63,0:04:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And if I said no?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.73,0:04:25.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やったな
Dialogue: 9,0:04:24.31,0:04:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you’ve done it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.74,0:04:31.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だからさ… あっ…
Dialogue: 9,0:04:29.86,0:04:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Like I said—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.76,0:05:25.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,真理亜！ 真理亜！\Nうん？
Dialogue: 9,0:05:23.05,0:05:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Maria! Maria!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.76,0:05:28.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ハア ハア…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.75,0:05:34.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,真理亜～っ
Dialogue: 9,0:05:33.17,0:05:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Maria!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.74,0:05:37.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あらあら どうしたの？
Dialogue: 9,0:05:35.81,0:05:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my, what’s wrong?
Dialogue: 9,0:05:37.53,0:05:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You’re just like a child right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.76,0:05:39.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まるで子供みたい\N今日の早季ったら
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.76,0:05:41.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,散歩に行きたいの
Dialogue: 9,0:05:40.61,0:05:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Take a walk with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.74,0:05:43.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,散歩？
Dialogue: 9,0:05:42.67,0:05:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,A walk?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.73,0:05:45.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お願い
Dialogue: 9,0:05:43.83,0:05:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 9,0:05:45.39,0:05:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.76,0:05:47.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いいわよ
Dialogue: 9,0:05:47.74,0:05:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,We’re going to take a walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.75,0:05:51.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,じゃあ 私たち 散歩してくるから\Nちょっと休憩してて
Dialogue: 9,0:05:50.34,0:05:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Let’s continue later.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.73,0:06:03.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ありがとう\N上手に描いてくれて うれしいわ
Dialogue: 9,0:05:58.86,0:05:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 9,0:05:59.94,0:06:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I really appreciate the beautiful portrait.
Dialogue: 9,0:06:16.62,0:06:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That’s why they went looking for green stones.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.73,0:06:19.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それで緑色の石を\N探しにいったんだって
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.73,0:06:24.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,くぬぎ林の渓流には\N結構あるみたいよ
Dialogue: 9,0:06:20.38,0:06:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I think there’s plenty near the mountain stream that runs through the little oak forest.
Dialogue: 9,0:06:24.64,0:06:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.77,0:06:27.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ねえ 何があったの？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.74,0:06:30.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ねえってば？
Dialogue: 9,0:06:28.51,0:06:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.73,0:06:41.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,答えなきゃ何もしてあげない
Dialogue: 9,0:06:39.79,0:06:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I won’t do anything unless you answer me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.73,0:06:51.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,早季も 早く！
Dialogue: 9,0:06:49.82,0:06:51.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on in!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.74,0:07:00.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ウフフ…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.75,0:07:48.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うふふ… あはは…！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.76,0:07:55.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ… 真理亜… 真理亜…
Dialogue: 9,0:07:55.97,0:07:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Maria…
Dialogue: 9,0:07:57.28,0:07:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Maria…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.75,0:08:00.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,人間の社会もまた
Dialogue: 9,0:07:58.62,0:08:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The scientists considered it their immediate duty
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.75,0:08:03.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ボノボ型の愛の社会に
Dialogue: 9,0:08:00.80,0:08:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,to create a society of love similar to that of bonobos.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.77,0:08:06.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,作り替えることが急務でした
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.76,0:08:15.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ね あれ
Dialogue: 9,0:08:14.22,0:08:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, look.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.77,0:08:21.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,きっと 覚がマネしたのよ
Dialogue: 9,0:08:20.26,0:08:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet Satoru copied it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.77,0:08:24.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いつの間にか あの子ったら\N瞬のマネばかりね
Dialogue: 9,0:08:22.14,0:08:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Lately he’s been trying so much to be like Shun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.74,0:08:28.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうだね… どうでもいいけど…
Dialogue: 9,0:08:25.73,0:08:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah…
Dialogue: 9,0:08:27.03,0:08:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s none of my business, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.78,0:08:33.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ねえ 楽しい？\Nえ…
Dialogue: 9,0:08:31.24,0:08:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey… is it fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.78,0:08:36.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,誰ともつきあわずにさ\N真理亜だけ そんな追いかけて
Dialogue: 9,0:08:33.86,0:08:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Being alone and chasing after Maria.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.78,0:08:39.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,楽しいって聞いてるの\Nあっ あ…
Dialogue: 9,0:08:37.39,0:08:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it really that fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.77,0:08:42.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,守も早く 恋人 作れば？
Dialogue: 9,0:08:40.33,0:08:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don’t you find someone too?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.76,0:08:47.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ねぇ 私たちも\N何か おそろいにしない？
Dialogue: 9,0:08:44.79,0:08:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, we should match, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.76,0:08:51.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,え？ うん いいけど…
Dialogue: 9,0:08:50.23,0:08:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine with me…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.75,0:08:54.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ん～ やっぱり やめ やめ
Dialogue: 9,0:08:53.91,0:08:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, let’s not.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.79,0:08:58.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なんか マネしてるみたいで\Nバカらしいもんね
Dialogue: 9,0:08:55.08,0:08:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,We’ll look dumb trying to copy them.
Dialogue: 9,0:09:02.58,0:09:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Wait, Saki!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.76,0:09:04.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ ねえ 待ってよ 早季
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.73,0:09:47.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何やってんだろう 私たち…
Dialogue: 9,0:09:44.39,0:09:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What on Earth are we doing?
Dialogue: 9,0:09:51.64,0:09:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I’ll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.81,0:09:53.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うん 大丈夫 行ってきま～す
Dialogue: 9,0:09:53.22,0:09:54.18,Default,,0,0,0,,See you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.80,0:09:55.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,行ってらっしゃい
Dialogue: 9,0:09:54.18,0:09:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye!
Dialogue: 9,0:10:04.59,0:10:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, cheer up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.78,0:10:07.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なあ 機嫌直してくれよ\Nどうしたんだよ 瞬？
Dialogue: 9,0:10:06.68,0:10:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What’s wrong, Shun?
Dialogue: 9,0:10:07.58,0:10:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing. I just need some time alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.80,0:10:09.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なんでもないよ\Nちょっと １人にしてくれ
Dialogue: 9,0:10:12.71,0:10:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It was my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.82,0:10:14.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺が悪かったよ
Dialogue: 9,0:10:14.38,0:10:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.79,0:10:16.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,頼むから…
Dialogue: 9,0:10:16.59,0:10:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Fault? What was?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.77,0:10:19.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,悪かった？ 何が？\Nそれは…
Dialogue: 9,0:10:18.56,0:10:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I…
Dialogue: 9,0:10:19.64,0:10:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Satoru, can we stop acting like we’re lovers now?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.78,0:10:22.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,覚 恋愛ごっこは\Nもういいだろう？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.80,0:10:26.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,僕は 君のお人形さんになるのに\Nいいかげん飽き飽きしたんだ
Dialogue: 9,0:10:23.17,0:10:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m fed up with being your little doll.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.80,0:10:30.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ… 分かった これからは…
Dialogue: 9,0:10:28.96,0:10:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I get it. I’ll change.
Dialogue: 9,0:10:30.60,0:10:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you don’t get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.82,0:10:34.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,分かってないね こんなふうに\N四六時中つきまとわれても
Dialogue: 9,0:10:32.27,0:10:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Being together around the clock is suffocating.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.81,0:10:38.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,暑苦しいだけなんだよ\N僕は１人になりたいんだ
Dialogue: 9,0:10:36.60,0:10:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to be alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.79,0:10:41.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だから 今日からは\Nお互い別行動にしよう
Dialogue: 9,0:10:39.16,0:10:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Let’s go our separate ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.80,0:10:46.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,じゃあな
Dialogue: 9,0:10:44.90,0:10:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.80,0:11:03.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうして？
Dialogue: 9,0:11:01.89,0:11:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Why…?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.79,0:11:14.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ 覚 見っけた エヘ…
Dialogue: 9,0:11:12.62,0:11:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,There y’are, Satoru.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.78,0:11:18.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,怜…
Dialogue: 9,0:11:17.36,0:11:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Rei…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.78,0:11:36.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ウフ…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.77,0:11:40.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あの様子だと 覚がふったのかな？
Dialogue: 9,0:11:38.17,0:11:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Does this mean Satoru dumped him?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.81,0:11:43.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,でも 瞬に夢中だったのに…\Nやっぱり 瞬かな？
Dialogue: 9,0:11:40.95,0:11:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,But he was all over Shun…
Dialogue: 9,0:11:42.97,0:11:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Was it Shun, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.81,0:11:45.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さあ…
Dialogue: 9,0:11:44.60,0:11:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.81,0:11:47.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なんだか バラバラになってくね…
Dialogue: 9,0:11:45.96,0:11:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,We’re drifting apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.78,0:11:52.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私と早季の間は永遠よね？
Dialogue: 9,0:11:49.95,0:11:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Saki and I will be together forever, right?
Dialogue: 9,0:11:52.54,0:11:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.80,0:12:07.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ！ 見て\Nああ？ あれ あれ！ あれ
Dialogue: 9,0:12:06.79,0:12:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, look!{background}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.78,0:12:09.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なに なに？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.80,0:12:15.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こっ これは 鏑木様\Nようこそいらっしゃいました
Dialogue: 9,0:12:12.00,0:12:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Heavens, Kaburagi-sama!
Dialogue: 9,0:12:13.65,0:12:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome to our class!
Dialogue: 9,0:12:15.68,0:12:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this a bad time?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.83,0:12:17.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,邪魔かな？\Nとっ とんでもございません
Dialogue: 9,0:12:17.05,0:12:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,N-Not at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.81,0:12:20.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ 鏑木様に\Nじきじきに来ていただけるとは
Dialogue: 9,0:12:18.61,0:12:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I cannot imagine an honor greater than having you visit my class.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.80,0:12:23.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これ以上に光栄なことは\Nございません
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.80,0:12:27.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ…\N何か お気にかかることでも？
Dialogue: 9,0:12:24.61,0:12:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there anything in particular on your mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.79,0:12:32.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いや ない たまには\N今後を担う子供たちの学びを…
Dialogue: 9,0:12:28.11,0:12:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,No, there isn’t.
Dialogue: 9,0:12:30.43,0:12:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I simply thought I’d check in on what our next generation is learning.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.81,0:12:35.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ねえねえ 鏑木肆星が\N何で ここに？
Dialogue: 9,0:12:32.87,0:12:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{mar}Hey, what’s Kaburagi Shisei doing here?
Dialogue: 9,0:12:35.69,0:12:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}On the contrary, I’d like to see a normal class.
Dialogue: 9,0:12:37.39,0:12:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{mar}I heard he could use his Cantus to\Nsplit the Earth in half if he focused.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.78,0:12:40.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あの人 本気で集中したら\N地球を真っ二つにするくらいの
Dialogue: 9,0:12:37.85,0:12:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Very well. This way, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.78,0:12:43.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,呪力があるんだって 知ってた？
Dialogue: 9,0:12:42.55,0:12:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{mar}Did you know that?
Dialogue: 9,0:12:43.76,0:12:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,No, but it wouldn’t surprise me if he could. He {\i1}is{\i0} the most powerful Cantus user.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.79,0:12:46.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ううん\Nでも 最強の呪力の持ち主だから
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.82,0:12:48.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それぐらい できても\N不思議はないけど…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.79,0:12:50.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ もう！ 何でもいいわ
Dialogue: 9,0:12:48.91,0:12:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, this is a great chance to draw some praise!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.81,0:12:52.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,とにかく\N認められるチャンスだもの
Dialogue: 9,0:13:02.74,0:13:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Not very exciting, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.81,0:13:04.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やっぱり地味すぎるのよね
Dialogue: 9,0:13:21.52,0:13:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you imagining to create it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.79,0:13:23.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どのようなイメージで\N作っているんだい？
Dialogue: 9,0:13:23.80,0:13:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir! I am imagining a perfectly flat lacquered board!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.81,0:13:26.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ はい！ あの…\Nゆがみの全くない 漆塗りの板を
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.81,0:13:28.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,イメージしています！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.78,0:13:33.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ふん… 難しい課題の１つだが\Nなかなかの出来だね
Dialogue: 9,0:13:29.15,0:13:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s a difficult exercise,
Dialogue: 9,0:13:32.57,0:13:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,but you’re doing quite well.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.82,0:13:35.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ありがとうございます！
Dialogue: 9,0:13:34.20,0:13:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.82,0:13:38.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その調子で励むように
Dialogue: 9,0:13:36.88,0:13:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep up the good work.
Dialogue: 9,0:13:38.69,0:13:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yessir!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.81,0:13:41.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はい！\Nさっすが 覚！
Dialogue: 9,0:13:40.05,0:13:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Good job, Satoru!
Dialogue: 9,0:14:00.73,0:14:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone was waiting for a historic encounter.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.80,0:14:03.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,誰もが 歴史的な出会いを期待した
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.80,0:14:06.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,瞬は いずれは鏑木肆星氏の
Dialogue: 9,0:14:04.19,0:14:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Shun was a genius expected to eventually inherit Kaburagi Shisei’s mantle.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.80,0:14:09.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,衣鉢を継ぐと目されている\N生徒である
Dialogue: 9,0:14:09.71,0:14:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,He could receive firsthand advice from the great master for the first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.82,0:14:13.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ここで 初めて じかに指導を\N受けることになるのだろうと
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.82,0:14:27.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああっ あの！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.81,0:14:29.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お待ちください\Nどうされたのですか？
Dialogue: 9,0:14:27.93,0:14:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, wait!
Dialogue: 9,0:14:28.91,0:14:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What is wrong?
Dialogue: 9,0:14:34.64,0:14:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Did something offend you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.81,0:14:37.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何か失礼でも\Nございましたでしょうか？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.82,0:14:40.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,えっ 本当ですか？
Dialogue: 9,0:14:38.98,0:14:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.79,0:14:43.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いっ いえ\N疑うなんて めっそうもない…
Dialogue: 9,0:14:41.20,0:14:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,No, not at all!
Dialogue: 9,0:14:42.05,0:14:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I would never doubt your judgment.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.79,0:14:45.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうなってるの？
Dialogue: 9,0:14:44.02,0:14:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{maria}What’s going on?
Dialogue: 9,0:14:44.02,0:14:46.26,Alternate,,0,0,0,,Yes… Yes…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.82,0:14:47.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なあ 何が起きたのかな？
Dialogue: 9,0:14:46.26,0:14:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.81,0:14:49.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,分かんない 分かんないけど…
Dialogue: 9,0:14:48.18,0:14:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I don’t know. I don’t know, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.80,0:14:55.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ええと 都合により\N今日の実技の時間は
Dialogue: 9,0:14:53.16,0:14:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Due to unforeseen circumstances, we’ll end today’s practice here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.80,0:14:58.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,中止になりました\Nえ～！
Dialogue: 9,0:14:58.73,0:15:00.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Please clean up your workspaces and return to your classrooms.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.79,0:15:00.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,各自 片づけて\N教室に戻ってください
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.84,0:15:03.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ねえ 覚 行こうよ ねえってば
Dialogue: 9,0:15:00.87,0:15:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Satoru, let’s go! Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.83,0:15:06.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,先に行ってくれよ 後から行くから
Dialogue: 9,0:15:04.25,0:15:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Go on ahead.
Dialogue: 9,0:15:05.46,0:15:07.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ll catch up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.81,0:15:10.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もう… ちぇっ
Dialogue: 9,0:15:09.32,0:15:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.82,0:15:14.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はいはい\N君たちも 早く片づけなさい
Dialogue: 9,0:15:11.87,0:15:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on! Clean up!
Dialogue: 9,0:15:24.82,0:15:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Let’s go, Shun.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.83,0:15:26.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,瞬 行かないの？
Dialogue: 9,0:15:26.72,0:15:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 9,0:15:34.58,0:15:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, that…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.79,0:15:36.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ねえ それ…
Dialogue: 9,0:15:37.49,0:15:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah…
Dialogue: 9,0:15:47.70,0:15:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.82,0:15:49.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さあさあ\N君たち 早く行きなさい！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.81,0:15:52.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,後は先生が片づけておくから
Dialogue: 9,0:15:50.66,0:15:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ll clean up the rest!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.81,0:15:59.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,瞬のことだから
Dialogue: 9,0:15:58.56,0:16:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I was surprised Shun didn’t stop the egg in midair when it fell.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.82,0:16:02.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,卵を空中でピッと止めると\N思ったんだけどなあ
Dialogue: 9,0:16:04.52,0:16:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Shun, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.82,0:16:06.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,瞬 大丈夫なのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.81,0:16:08.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ 大したことない
Dialogue: 9,0:16:06.84,0:16:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I’m fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.82,0:16:10.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ちょっと疲れただけだから
Dialogue: 9,0:16:09.08,0:16:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m just a little tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.81,0:16:14.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もう 早退すれば？
Dialogue: 9,0:16:12.99,0:16:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Want to go home early?
Dialogue: 9,0:16:14.77,0:16:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Nah, I’m fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.81,0:16:16.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いや 本当に平気
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.82,0:16:20.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なんか…\N何？
Dialogue: 9,0:16:18.96,0:16:20.27,Default,,0,0,0,,This…
Dialogue: 9,0:16:20.27,0:16:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.82,0:16:25.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なんか 懐かしい感じ\N最近 ５人揃ってなかったから
Dialogue: 9,0:16:21.22,0:16:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,This feels so nostalgic!
Dialogue: 9,0:16:23.20,0:16:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,We’ve been kind of apart recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.84,0:16:32.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,アッハハ… ハハハ…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.84,0:17:30.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,瞬！
Dialogue: 9,0:17:28.95,0:17:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Shun!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.84,0:17:33.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうしたの？
Dialogue: 9,0:17:31.98,0:17:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.84,0:17:35.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,早季…
Dialogue: 9,0:17:34.44,0:17:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Saki…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.83,0:17:39.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,来るな！
Dialogue: 9,0:17:38.44,0:17:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Don’t come closer!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.85,0:17:41.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ… どうして？
Dialogue: 9,0:17:40.74,0:17:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.83,0:17:44.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ごめん でも１人になりたいんだ
Dialogue: 9,0:17:42.74,0:17:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry… but I want to be alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.82,0:17:47.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,１人に？\Nああ
Dialogue: 9,0:17:45.35,0:17:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Alone?
Dialogue: 9,0:17:46.84,0:17:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 9,0:17:47.67,0:17:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that why you broke up with Satoru?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.82,0:17:49.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だから 覚とも別れたの？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.81,0:17:51.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まあ そうかな…
Dialogue: 9,0:17:50.56,0:17:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.81,0:17:54.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,友達を捨ててまで\N１人になりたいの？
Dialogue: 9,0:17:52.29,0:17:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to be alone so badly that you’d abandon your friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.85,0:17:58.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それは 説明しても\N早季には分からないよ
Dialogue: 9,0:17:54.92,0:17:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if I explained, I don’t think you’d understand.
Dialogue: 9,0:18:06.60,0:18:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I don’t think we’ll be able to meet for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.84,0:18:08.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しばらく 会えなくなると思う
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.83,0:18:10.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,えっ どういうこと？
Dialogue: 9,0:18:10.17,0:18:11.45,Default,,0,0,0,,How come?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.81,0:18:12.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,当分 学校へは行けない
Dialogue: 9,0:18:11.45,0:18:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ll be out of school for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.85,0:18:14.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,僕は療養しなきゃならないんだ
Dialogue: 9,0:18:13.62,0:18:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to get special treatment.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.83,0:18:16.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,病気なの？
Dialogue: 9,0:18:15.45,0:18:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sick?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.80,0:18:20.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うん 病気っていうか…\Nどう言えば分かるかな
Dialogue: 9,0:18:17.70,0:18:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Sick… well…
Dialogue: 9,0:18:19.54,0:18:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I don’t know how to explain it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.82,0:18:22.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,体の病気ではないんだ
Dialogue: 9,0:18:21.19,0:18:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s not my body that’s sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.84,0:18:26.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,じゃあ 僕はもう行かなきゃ
Dialogue: 9,0:18:25.28,0:18:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, I have to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.83,0:18:30.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,待って！\Nお見舞いに行ってもいい？
Dialogue: 9,0:18:27.43,0:18:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 9,0:18:29.17,0:18:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I come visit you?
Dialogue: 9,0:18:31.60,0:18:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I don’t think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.83,0:18:33.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうかな？\Nえっ？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.85,0:18:36.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,僕は もう家には いられないし
Dialogue: 9,0:18:35.08,0:18:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I can’t stay at home anymore, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.86,0:18:38.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ… どこに行くの？
Dialogue: 9,0:18:37.73,0:18:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you going, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.82,0:18:41.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,療養のための\N小さなバンガローだよ
Dialogue: 9,0:18:39.21,0:18:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,To a small bungalow, for rehabilitation.
Dialogue: 9,0:18:41.68,0:18:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.83,0:18:43.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それ どこにあるの？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.81,0:18:46.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ごめん 場所は\N言ってはいけないことになってる
Dialogue: 9,0:18:44.32,0:18:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry. I can’t tell you that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.85,0:18:52.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,瞬 本当に\N１人ぼっちになっちゃったの？
Dialogue: 9,0:18:49.31,0:18:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Shun, will you really be all alone?
Dialogue: 9,0:18:52.73,0:18:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What about Subaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.80,0:18:54.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,すばるは どうしたの？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.86,0:18:57.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,家にいるよ 散歩したくなったから
Dialogue: 9,0:18:55.15,0:18:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,He’s at home.
Dialogue: 9,0:18:56.47,0:18:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I just wanted to take a walk, so I snuck out alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.86,0:18:59.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,１人で こっそり\N抜け出してきたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.83,0:19:03.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私 どうすれば瞬の力になれるの？
Dialogue: 9,0:19:00.37,0:19:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there any way I can help you?
Dialogue: 9,0:19:09.85,0:19:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Shun, I’ve always lo—
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.86,0:19:13.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,瞬 私 ずっと瞬のことが…
Dialogue: 9,0:19:13.71,0:19:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Saki, I should tell you at least this much.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.81,0:19:15.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,早季 迷ったんだけどね
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.86,0:19:18.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やっぱり このことだけは\N言っておいた方がいいと思う
Dialogue: 9,0:19:20.55,0:19:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember the summer camp two years ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.83,0:19:22.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,２年前の夏季キャンプ 覚えてる？
Dialogue: 9,0:19:23.13,0:19:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 9,0:19:24.82,0:19:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Our Cantus was sealed by Rijin,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.82,0:19:27.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,僕らは離塵師に\N呪力を凍結されたけど
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.84,0:19:31.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,でも それは\Nうまく隠し通せたと思ってた
Dialogue: 9,0:19:29.14,0:19:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,but we thought that we managed to hide that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.21,0:19:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 9,0:19:33.32,0:19:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,We didn’t.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.83,0:19:36.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,でも そうじゃなかったんだ\N｢そうじゃない｣って？
Dialogue: 9,0:19:35.15,0:19:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.83,0:19:40.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,多分 全部バレてたんだ\Nどういう意図かは分からないけど
Dialogue: 9,0:19:37.47,0:19:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I’d say they knew it all along.
Dialogue: 9,0:19:39.50,0:19:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I don’t know why, but I think they\Nsimply decided to delay punishing us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.85,0:19:43.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,単に処分を\N保留にされてただけなんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.84,0:19:46.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,言ってる意味\Nよく分かんないんだけど
Dialogue: 9,0:19:44.09,0:19:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m not sure where this is going.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.81,0:19:49.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,僕らは ずっと監視されていたんだ
Dialogue: 9,0:19:47.63,0:19:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,We’ve probably been under constant surveillance.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.86,0:19:54.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今さら こんな警告をしても\N意味ないかもしれない
Dialogue: 9,0:19:51.98,0:19:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I don’t think I really have to warn you by now,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.83,0:19:58.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,でも 早季 猫には気をつけて
Dialogue: 9,0:19:55.92,0:19:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,but, Saki, watch out for the cats.
Dialogue: 9,0:19:58.61,0:20:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Cats? You mean the Copycats?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.85,0:20:01.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,猫？ ネコダマシのこと？
Dialogue: 9,0:20:02.47,0:20:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, take this.{important plot item!}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.84,0:20:04.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうだ これ あげるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.83,0:20:10.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ 何？ これ
Dialogue: 9,0:20:10.02,0:20:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What’s this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.85,0:20:14.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,猫よけのおまじない\N僕が作ったんだ
Dialogue: 9,0:20:11.14,0:20:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,A charm against the cats.
Dialogue: 9,0:20:13.09,0:20:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I made it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.84,0:20:16.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,すばるとおそろいなの？
Dialogue: 9,0:20:15.46,0:20:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Subaru has the same, doesn’t he?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.84,0:20:19.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,アハ…
Dialogue: 9,0:20:27.55,0:20:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Please let the others know, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.83,0:20:30.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,僕が言ったこと\Nみんなに伝えてほしいんだ
Dialogue: 9,0:20:39.34,0:20:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Silly dog. I told you not to follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.83,0:20:42.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,馬鹿だな あれほど\Nついてくるなって言ったのに
